Zero point energy                ...      0.44858401 Eh     281.49 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.02149513 Eh      13.49 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
